{"article_id":"BJX07Fd4FewxBxV5","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Mattis Takes Swipe At Trump :","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"' I Earned My Spurs On The Battlefield '","depth":2},{"id":2,"text":"President Trump fired him","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"( after he submitted his resignation )","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"and earlier this week reportedly called him `` the world 's most overrated general , ''","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"but former Defense Secretary Jim Mattis had a few barbs of his own to sling in a speech","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"he gave in New York on Thursday .","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"Delivering the keynote address at the 74th Alfred E. Smith Memorial Foundation Dinner ,","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"Mattis","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"- a retired four-star U.S. Marine general -","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"said","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"he felt","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"he had finally `` achieved greatness . ''","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"`` I 'm not just an overrated general ,","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"I am the greatest , the world 's most overrated , ''","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"he said to laughter .","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"`` I 'm honored to be considered that by Donald Trump ,","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"because he also called Meryl Streep an overrated actress , ''","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"Mattis continued .","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"`` So , I guess","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"I 'm the Meryl Streep of generals .","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"Frankly that sounds pretty good to me . ''","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"The jibes were a departure for Mattis ,","depth":5},{"id":23,"text":"whose book Call Sign Chaos :","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"Learning to Lead ,","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"published last month ,","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"was met with criticism from some","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"who said","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"he had pulled punches","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"in characterizing the president 's erratic leadership style .","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"In an interview with NPR","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"promoting his book ,","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"Mattis declined to discuss his relationship with Trump .","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"`` I do n't discuss sitting presidents , ''","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"Mattis said .","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"`` I believe","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"that you owe a period of quiet . ''","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"Thursday 's annual gala ,","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"named after the former New York governor","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"who won the Democratic nomination for president in 1928 ,","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"was hosted this year by Cardinal Timothy Dolan , the archbishop of New York .","depth":5},{"id":41,"text":"Mattis said","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"he had been asked what he thought of Trump 's remarks ,","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"which reportedly came during a White House meeting with congressional Democrats on Wednesday .","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"`` I earned my spurs on the battlefield ...","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"Donald Trump earned his spurs in a letter from a doctor , ''","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"he said in a reference to a medical deferment for bone spurs","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"that kept Trump from serving in the military during the Vietnam War .","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"Although Trump 's nickname for Mattis was `` mad dog ''","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"- a nickname","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"the former general despised -","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"Mattis said","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"these days he feels more like `` an emotional support animal . ''","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"`` And that 's really great ,","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"because now the airlines allow me to fly for free , ''","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"But Mattis quickly moved on from the jokes","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"and picked up a more serious tone ,","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"citing a speech","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"that Abraham Lincoln gave in 1838 to the Young Men 's Lyceum of Springfield , Ill .","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"In it , Lincoln `` observed great nations crumble for one of two reasons , ''","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"the first being foreign invasion ,","depth":14},{"id":62,"text":"Mattis said ,","depth":14},{"id":63,"text":"which the future president dismissed as `` inconceivable . ''","depth":13},{"id":64,"text":"The second ,","depth":14},{"id":65,"text":"he said ,","depth":15},{"id":66,"text":"paraphrasing Lincoln ,","depth":15},{"id":67,"text":"`` was corrosion from within","depth":14},{"id":68,"text":"- the rot , the viciousness , the lassitude , the ignorance . ''","depth":14},{"id":69,"text":"`` Anarchy is one potential consequence of all this .","depth":13},{"id":70,"text":"The other is the rise of an ambitious leader ,","depth":16},{"id":71,"text":"unfettered by conscience , or precedent or decency ,","depth":16},{"id":72,"text":"who would make himself supreme , ''","depth":15},{"id":73,"text":"he said .","depth":14},{"id":74,"text":"Decrying the lack of bipartisanship ,","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"Mattis warned of a `` national paralysis ''","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"that has `` supplanted trust and empathy with suspicion and contempt . ''","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"`` We have scorched our opponents with language","depth":13},{"id":78,"text":"that precludes compromise","depth":13},{"id":79,"text":"and we have brushed aside the possibility","depth":13},{"id":80,"text":"that the person","depth":15},{"id":81,"text":"with whom we disagree","depth":15},{"id":82,"text":"might actually sometimes be right , ''","depth":14},{"id":83,"text":"he said .","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"`` We owe a debt to all","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"who fought for liberty ,","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"including those","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"who tonight serve in the far corners of our planet , among them the American men and women","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"supporting our Kurdish allies , ''","depth":13},{"id":89,"text":"the retired general said .","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"In conclusion , Mattis again paraphrased Lincoln , this time that president 's famous Second Inaugural speech ,","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"delivered in the closing days of the Civil War :","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"`` With malice for none and charity for all , let us restore trust in one another . ''","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":185,"left":94,"right":184,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":94,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":184,"left":113,"right":183,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":113,"left":98,"right":112,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":98,"left":96,"right":97,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":96,"left":95,"right":4,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":95,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":97,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":112,"left":103,"right":111,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":101,"right":102,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":101,"left":7,"right":100,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":100,"left":99,"right":10,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":99,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":102,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":111,"left":105,"right":110,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":105,"left":104,"right":15,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":110,"left":107,"right":109,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":107,"left":106,"right":18,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"N